t-hart updated how 
``from-ssv``
 works to better fit real-world tasks (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/845] #845
)
andrasio fixed some path issues in 
``inc``
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/848] #848
)
andrasio also added the new 
``group-by``
 command (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/857] #857
)
jdvr connect Nu to the local platform recycle bin, so 
``rm``
 can now move to Trash (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/854] #854
)
detegr fixed a panic inside of the 
``enter``
 command (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/862] #862
)
vsoch has continued building plugins in Go and Python and 
[link: https://vsoch.github.io/2019/nushell-golang-plugin-library/] documenting the process
wycats continued to improve how commands are colored (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/864] #864
)
Charles-Schleich added more docs (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/858] #858
)
