)
jdvr connect Nu to the local platform recycle bin, so 
``rm``
 can now move to Trash (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/854] #854
)
detegr fixed a panic inside of the 
``enter``
 command (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/862] #862
)
vsoch has continued building plugins in Go and Python and 
[link: https://vsoch.github.io/2019/nushell-golang-plugin-library/] documenting the process
wycats continued to improve how commands are colored (
